cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper deals with the problem of lifelong learning for generative models, specifically in the context of conditional image generation. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on generative models and image generation, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
